Package: gnome-encfs-manager
Architecture: any
Recommends: wmctrl, libnotify-bin
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, encfs, fuse
Description: An easy to use manager and mounter for encfs stashes
 The Gnome Encfs Manager is a manager and mounter for encfs stashes. It features:
  * an easy and quick to use tray icon inspired by Cryptkeeper but using the AppIndicator API
  * Gnome keyring support
  * per-stash configuration for all features
  * automatic mounting, when a stash gets available
    (e.g. when you insert a usb drive containing a configured stash)
  * an intuitive interface to create, configure and import stashes
  * automount-at-startup support
